user.biography: We are Mebie Baby! We offer modern + simple designed Swaddle Blankets and Baby basics.  collabs@mebiebaby.com #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, baby and indoor.

node.text: When we started making the organic footies we just had them in three sizes. We now have them in newborn up to 3T and I love that babies and toddlers can enjoy them. Do you put your toddlers in footies? #mebiebaby

node.text:
Let’s do a quick Mebie Baby weekend giveaway! Winner will get $150 store credit. All you need to do to enter is:
1. Like this photo + follow @mebie.baby 
2. Tell me which color of gown is your favorite!
3. Tag your friends!
Giveaway will end July 19th at midnight. #mebiebaby 

We will announce winner here, please watch for fake accounts and do not follow any links.

Winner is @ricechrisspy

node.text: Who’s excited to have organic footies back? We sure are! They are one of the favorite items here at Mebie Baby. #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 15, 2021.

node.text: Organic cotton is here! We’re so excited for the new color, navy! Also, sizing in the footies now goes up to 3T! Grip on the feet from size 6-12 to 3T. Yay!! #mebiebaby

node.text: Did your babies like to be swaddled or arms free? My two did not love being swaddled. That was before Mebie Baby stretch swaddles, so I hope baby on the way will enjoy it. 🥰 #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 13, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, baby and indoor.

node.text: Who’s ready for an organic cotton restock? We will be restocking most colors of gowns and footies, the release will be Thursday at 8:00 am MST! The colors we have are, dusty rose, vanilla, oatmeal, mustard, plum, green and a navy! #mebiebaby
